"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/384907","Ministry of Defence","false","2015-06-29","<p>The Ministry of Defence has commissioned a review into reprovision of the Household Cavalry Mounted Regiment that will investigate, amongst other things, the issues raised by the right hon. Member.</p><p> </p>","Milton Keynes North","Mark Lancaster","3843 ; 3844","2015-06-29T15:21:34.217Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/384907/answer","Biography information for Mark Lancaster","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/384907/answer",,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/384907/answer",,,,,"11","Defence","Defence","2015-06-23","Wellington Barracks","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Defence, what recent assessment his Department has made of the condition of Wellington Barracks; and what plans he has for the future use of those barracks.","false","Biography information for Sir Nicholas Soames","Mid Sussex","Sir Nicholas Soames","3900"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/384908","Ministry of Defence","false","2015-06-29","<p>The Ministry of Defence continues to engage with key stakeholders while we explore the possibility of reprovision for the Household Cavalry Mounted Regiment.</p>","Milton Keynes North","Mark Lancaster",,"2015-06-29T15:23:24.137Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/384908/answer","Biography information for Mark Lancaster","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/384908/answer",,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/384908/answer",,,,,"11","Defence","Defence","2015-06-23","Household Cavalry Mounted Regiment","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Defence, what discussions he has had with (a) London local authorities, (b) the Royal Parks and (c) the Mayor of London on the construction of a new barracks for the Household Cavalry Mounted Regiment; and if he will make a statement.","false","Biography information for Sir Nicholas Soames","Mid Sussex","Sir Nicholas Soames","3845"
