"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/385096","Ministry of Justice","false","2015-07-01","<p>Calculating release dates is not individually specified in the Directory of Services used in the National Offender Management Service. It is not therefore possible to provide reliable information on the cost or resource employed in this particular activity.</p>","South West Bedfordshire","Andrew Selous",,"2015-07-01T14:54:16.087Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/385096/answer","Biography information for Andrew Selous","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/385096/answer",,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/385096/answer",,,,,"54","Justice","Justice","2015-06-23","Prisoners' Release","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Justice, how much is spent by HM Prison (a) Leeds and (b) Wakefield to calculate the release date of prisoners; and how many people are employed to carry out that calculation.","false","Biography information for Philip Davies","Shipley","Philip Davies","3723"
